('55d1e743-58c7-4ba8-865e-14e84265dc0e', 'Transparent Labs Fat Burner: Evidence-Based Thermogenic', 'Every ingredient clinically dosed and clearly labeled. The PhysiqueSeries Fat Burner includes mood support via 5-HTP, setting it apart from stim-heavy competitors.', 'Forslean (500mg) activates lipase to release stored body fat. Green Tea Extract (500mg) provides EGCG for fat oxidation. 5-HTP (150mg) supports serotonin and mood during caloric restriction.', ARRAY['Fully transparent dosing', 'Clinically backed ingredients', 'Mood support during dieting', 'No proprietary blends'], 'Take 4 capsules daily. Start with 2 to assess tolerance.', ARRAY['Contains synephrine (stimulant)', 'Premium price', '4 capsules per serving'], 'Evidence-based fitness enthusiasts who want transparent dosing and mood support during cuts.', 'Instant Knockout for more thermogenic power. Burn Lab Pro for stimulant-free.', 'Q: Is synephrine safe? A: Studies show it is safe at recommended doses but consult a doctor if you have heart conditions. Q: Does 5-HTP help with cravings? A: Yes, by supporting serotonin it can reduce carb and sugar cravings.', 8.6, '[{"name": "Ryan M.", "rating": 5, "text": "The 5-HTP addition is genius. My mood stays positive even deep into a calorie deficit.", "verified": true, "date": "2026-01-11"}, {"name": "Nicole J.", "rating": 4, "text": "Love the transparency. I can see exactly what I am putting in my body.", "verified": true, "date": "2025-12-23"}]'::jsonb),

('15cce14b-8336-4f2c-ab47-8c39cf3a44df', 'Burn Lab Pro: Best Stimulant-Free Fat Burner', 'A unique stimulant-free approach combining fat burning with muscle preservation. Ideal for those who cannot tolerate caffeine or train in the evening.', 'Forslean (250mg) triggers fat cell release. HMB (1500mg) prevents muscle breakdown during dieting. Capsimax (50mg) boosts calorie burning. Chromium controls blood sugar.', ARRAY['100% stimulant-free', 'Preserves muscle while burning fat', 'Clean label with no additives', 'Can be taken any time of day'], 'Take 3 capsules daily before exercise or first thing in the morning.', ARRAY['Slower results than stimulant-based options', 'Premium pricing', 'Only available online'], 'Perfect for those sensitive to stimulants, evening exercisers, and anyone wanting fat loss without jitters.', 'Instant Knockout for stimulant-based option. Trimtone for simple one-pill alternative.', 'Q: Can I take it at night? A: Yes, no stimulants means no sleep disruption. Q: Does HMB really preserve muscle? A: Multiple studies show HMB reduces muscle protein breakdown during caloric restriction.', 8.4, '[{"name": "Tom K.", "rating": 5, "text": "Finally a fat burner I can take without feeling wired. Lost 10 lbs while keeping my strength.", "verified": true, "date": "2026-01-09"}, {"name": "Maria E.", "rating": 4, "text": "Great for evening workouts. No sleep issues and steady fat loss.", "verified": true, "date": "2025-12-21"}]'::jsonb),

('5de66d78-385b-4f9f-bb34-f704b925598b', 'Burn-XT: Best Budget Fat Burner', 'The Amazon best-seller for good reason: simple, effective formula at an unbeatable price. Nothing fancy, just proven ingredients that work.', 'Acetyl L-Carnitine (700mg) shuttles fat for energy. Green Tea Extract (450mg) provides EGCG. Caffeine Anhydrous (270mg) drives thermogenesis. Capsimax and BioPerine enhance absorption.', ARRAY['Very affordable', 'Amazon best-seller', 'Simple effective formula', 'Good ALCAR dose for energy'], 'Take 2 capsules in the morning with food. Do not take after 3pm.', ARRAY['270mg caffeine may cause jitters', 'Basic formula', 'May cause anxiety in sensitive people'], 'Budget-conscious dieters who want proven basics without paying for premium branding.', 'Instant Knockout for premium option. Trimtone for lower caffeine.', 'Q: Why is it so popular on Amazon? A: Great price, effective basics, and thousands of positive reviews build trust. Q: Is 270mg caffeine a lot? A: About 3 cups of coffee. Start with 1 capsule if sensitive.', 8.0, '[{"name": "Steven R.", "rating": 5, "text": "Best value fat burner period. Lost 15 lbs combined with diet and exercise.", "verified": true, "date": "2026-01-07"}, {"name": "Tina L.", "rating": 4, "text": "Gets the job done for the price. The caffeine kick is solid for morning workouts.", "verified": true, "date": "2025-12-18"}]'::jsonb),

